b7bc95.jpg&h=8d9e2cab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c307833871af983492c454dfb5747d09c02801ed","tid":178532,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>甲鐵城出之後覺得幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n近年幾套話題性爭議性大既機械人動畫我咁排<br />\n<br />\naz=天使龍&gt;革命機&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 超時空三角</blockquote><br />\n我排天使龍&gt;az&gt;delta&gt;vvv<br />\n天使龍一開始就對佢冇期望 對福田仲有偏見 但意外地搞笑 反而覺得佢冇咩爭議<br />\naz一期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndelta前半有幾場都打得幾正 不過後半除佐良平同界人一齊死之外 我而家完全係0印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nvvv經過罪冠之後就完全失望 所以某程度上大河內冇令我失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真我覺得az同delta幾可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想機戰洗底<br />\n但vvv就冇拯救既價值 所以skip佐比天使龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcef97c52d9aa492cc95295e86e948ae2c88b81","tid":178532,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"男吸啖血就算數<br />\n女就要屌西<br />\n好西利既設定"},{"pid":"18ae8989a6f1e3025df5b9141b480bafa67eb248","tid":178532,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>甲鐵城出之後覺得幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n近年幾套話題性爭議性大既機械人動畫我咁排<br />\n<br />\naz=天使龍&gt;革命機&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 超時空三角</blockquote><br />\n我排天使龍&gt;az&gt;delta&gt;vvv<br />\n天使龍一開始就對佢冇期望 對福田仲有偏見 但意外地搞笑 反而覺得佢冇咩爭議<br />\naz一期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndelta前半有幾場都打得幾正 不過後半除佐良平同界人一齊死之外 我而家完全係0印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal